name: Fly High (Early Access)
description:
Fly High is a game where you dodge obstacles in different themes. The longer you live the more points you earn. Spend those points in the game's shop to buy skins. This is an early access version of Fly High (the actual version is still in development), so please report any bugs to the official One Alone Studios Discord Server: https://discord.gg/uKeXtWhc

Youtube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxevdnpC1oi91YU67xr1WWg
